{"tid":1880590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"收押所外 市民高呼：手足我愛你","createTime":"2020-02-15T03:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T03:56:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd1b176fb9974fde29a954df19f1df4bf631991","tid":1880590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:22:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/PJK6P4QGNDPOWA4GV363OAHTB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FPJK6P4QGNDPOWA4GV363OAHTB4%2F&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=8e92a9b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FPJK6P4QGNDPOWA4GV363OAHTB4%2F&h=5981d865\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/PJK6P4QGNDPOWA4GV363OAHTB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n收押所外 市民高呼：手足我愛你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200215/large/1581697514_1ac6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200215%2Flarge%2F1581697514_1ac6.gif&h=3945fe84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人舉起「手足，我愛你」標語，希望抗爭者知道未被忘記。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】個多月來港人雖忙於抗疫，抗爭之心仍未冷卻，昨日是情人節，社民連與數百人戴上口罩聚集在荔枝角收押所外，「光復香港時代革命」黑旗再次飄揚，參加者舉起「撐手足，撐到底」等標語，高呼「手足我愛你」過百次，聲援高牆內的抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n集會由社民連發起，向現場人士派發紅玫瑰，梁國雄（長毛）發言指，被捕者在獄中未必得到足夠保護，非常擔心其健康，祝願手足保重。梁又指林鄭欲以疫症停止抗爭，然而醫護人員罷工，抗爭者亦會跟香港人一起抗爭到底。他又表示，情人節起源與反抗暴政有關，故情人節來到為過百位被捕者致敬，又帶領參加者高呼過百次「手足，我愛你」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防暴警舉藍旗清場<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：香港家居隔離者擅往公院求診<br />\n<br />\n有參加者派明信片讓人向被捕人士訴說心聲，有人向收押所揮動手機燈和巨型心形燈牌，並高叫「釋放義士，還我公義」等口號，懲教處人員在收押所外戒備，軍裝警則在遠處戒備。<br />\n<br />\n參加者鄧女士自言曾是不問世事的老人家，連問責官員名字都不知道，<span style=\"color: orange;\">感謝年輕人啟發她上街遊行。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">她認為抗爭者只是行使公民權益抗議，而非暴動，「佢哋係香港人嘅希望，希望佢哋冇事行返出嚟」，指摘警方藉濫捕阻止市民行使公民權利。</span><br />\n<br />\n另一位參加者C小姐以手機播放句子「你能擁抱你的所愛，他只能在獄裏感慨」，她說：<span style=\"color: orange;\">「我哋一直以嚟嘅成果都係手足犧牲得來，所以喺任何節日都唔應該忘記手足」</span>，她已視被捕者為家人，即使互不相識，仍希望對方知道未被忘記。<br />\n<br />\n活動在9時半結束，有軍裝警員呼籲現場人士離開，近10時防暴警到場舉藍旗，驅趕參加者。其後有人於通州西街馬路以花盆、垃圾桶等雜物擺設路障，迅即有防暴警及速龍小隊警員趕到清理並喝斥現場人士，群眾陸續散去。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李詠希、陳詠恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200215/large/1581697514_c03b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200215%2Flarge%2F1581697514_c03b.gif&h=ec7fcb5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批市民昨在荔枝角收押所外集會，聲援被捕人士。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232c8da94fa4f00b991a29b1fc93f5dca28df814","tid":1880590,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"有銀髮族 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ddfdcbe667feb9cbf9d235cd47fed7584547f0","tid":1880590,"uid":72654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4684050dff4e0e342cb8ae9f80366a6d4c0fbbaf","tid":1880590,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"得銀髮族同毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75a1330cd6fecfeaa0